content: The bachelor party in Miami is going to be a blast! We're planning a boat tour, a night out in South Beach, and a few other activities, but we're also leaving some room for spontaneity. It's going to be a fun weekend with the guys. By the way, I've been thinking about my travel photos from the past year, and I realized I have three albums on Google Photos - one from my Vegas trip, one from my SF trip, and one from my Tahoe trip. I need to get around to captioning them all still.
